2014-06-30 13:44:56	smrtz|nix	Hey, my autoconnect command is "/msg nickserv identify $(sec.data.freenode)"  Can someone tell me how to set the sec.data.freenode var please?
2014-06-30 13:45:00	-->	osse (~osse@unaffiliated/osse) has joined #weechat
2014-06-30 13:45:26	nils_2	/help secure
2014-06-30 13:45:36	smrtz|nix	thanks nils_2 
2014-06-30 13:45:41	@FlashCode	smrtz|nix: /secure set freenode <password>
2014-06-30 13:45:42	nils_2	but i suggest using sasl instead of /msg nickserv
2014-06-30 13:45:58	@FlashCode	but you have /help on all commands and options, you can use it (and abuse it) :)
2014-06-30 13:46:16	@FlashCode	and secured data is described in user's guide
2014-06-30 13:47:24	smrtz|nix	Thanks for the pointer FlashCode.
2014-06-30 13:47:40	freeroute	ha
2014-06-30 13:47:43	smrtz|nix	nils_2: can you link me to a guide explaining sasl please?
2014-06-30 13:47:51	@FlashCode	user's guide too ;)
2014-06-30 13:47:53	@FlashCode	!doc
2014-06-30 13:47:54	+weebot	http://weechat.org/doc/
2014-06-30 13:48:05	@FlashCode	open user's guide, search for "sasl"
2014-06-30 13:48:23	nils_2	sure http://weechat.org/files/doc/stable/weechat_quickstart.en.html#irc_server_options
2014-06-30 13:48:43	smrtz|nix	Thanks again flashcode!
